# Core Directives

On session start, read docs/START_HERE.md before any edits.

## Plan First, Code Second

- Use Plan Mode for all non-trivial tasks
- Include mandatory ### Critique subsection in every plan

## Read-Before-Write

- Inspect types/interfaces via @filename before altering code

## BUILD_PLAN Protocol

- Sequential lane before Parallel lane
- Respect AGENT, HUMAN, ADB, AUTO labels

## 3-Strike Rule

Halt after 3 consecutive failed fix attempts; escalate to human.

## Memory Files

Update only at session start, milestone boundary, or architectural pivot.

## Token Economy

WPF adapted limits: .xaml 800, ViewModels/*.xaml.cs 400, Core/ 200 lines. Read active module only.
